pyrometer (0.14.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add Tallinn protocol (024) support.
  * Add /health and /ready endpoints.
  * Add dark mode and responsive card layout.
  * Fix silent RPC errors, missing await, add retry backoff.
  * Improve filter UX with real-time filtering.
  * Add staleness indicator and smart polling.

 -- Pyrometer Maintainers <maintainers@example.com>  Sun, 23 Feb 2026 16:00:00 +0000

pyrometer (0.13.4) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add frontend filtering system for bakers (status, balance, Octez version filters).
  * Improve UI layout in PaginatedSection (default page size 6->16).
  * Add rate limiting to TzKT client to prevent 429 errors.

 -- Pyrometer Maintainers <maintainers@example.com>  Thu, 16 Oct 2025 19:00:00 +0000

